### 运行内置评测集（忠实度 / 相关性）
POST http://localhost:18030/eval/run
Content-Type: application/json

### 再次运行（应命中响应缓存，cached=true）
POST http://localhost:18030/eval/run
Content-Type: application/json

### 清空响应缓存
POST http://localhost:18030/eval/cache/clear

### 自定义评测用例
POST http://localhost:18030/eval/run
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "id": "custom-1",
    "question": "OTA升级失败一般是什么原因？",
    "evidenceKeywords": ["网络", "签名"],
    "relevanceKeywords": ["OTA", "失败"]
  }
]
